Session bootstrap cursor for `<project>`. Target ~30-50 lines maximum. This
file is NOT history, NOT a decisions archive, NOT an open-threads log.

> **Contrast with other files.**
> - Locked decisions live in `_living_decisions.md`
> - Design intent lives in `_living_design.md`
> - Raw untriaged capture lives in `_scratchpad.md`
> - Current code state lives in `_aware_*.md` (its own evolving category)
> - Current focus is any intake entry with `status: in_progress`
>
> This file only holds the session-start cursor: what to read first, what
> to do next, what (if anything) is blocking.

## Currently focused on

**Focus:** (none - set via `/devlead focus <intake-id>`, which flips the entry's `status` to `in_progress`)
**Last touched:** (set on first session)

## Read at session start

1. `devlead_docs/_intake_*.md` - scan for `status: in_progress` to find current focus
2. `devlead_docs/_aware_features.md` - current feature inventory (auto-derived)
3. `devlead_docs/_aware_design.md` - current module inventory (auto-derived)
4. `devlead_docs/_scratchpad.md` - untriaged raw capture
5. `devlead_docs/_living_decisions.md` - locked decisions archive

